{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were transported, about 1,400 people, but I think at that day, all the-- on the Polish border there must have been, I think, about 40,000 people who were deported from Germany into Poland.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They asked us, where do you want to go?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And well, we really had nobody where to go, but my father served in the Austrian army in the first World War.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father had a very good memory for people he ever met.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he tried-- keep in touch with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he knew that his mother's family came from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a nearer city to go, really, so we said to go to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put us on a train to Cracow, and there we were on the railroad station all of a sudden standing there with basically no place to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Somebody called a family who were very common in Cracow and very, very wealthy and asked them if they had-- they have four people here, if they need quarter-- if they, if they would take them in.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And their name was Wasserberger, name of the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, W-A-S-S-E-R-B-E-R-G-E-R, Wasserberger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had flour mills, and they had, if I remember right, a monopoly for rice for the import into China.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very, very-- it's big business people, very nice family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was started by an old man, we call him the old Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wasserberger, and he had three sons and one daughter but owned the business in different areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and that Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wasserberger said, well, she would take them in if the man who called her would personally guarantee for us, guarantee for us, because obviously they had a very, a very nice home.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
